[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has a maximum 1\H opening bid.

NORTH would have made a Limit Raise in \Hs, but after WEST's overcall she 
makes a Support Cue-bid instead.

SOUTH thinks there may be a slam and bids 4NT Blackwood to check for Aces. When NORTH admits to one Ace 
SOUTH bids the slam.}

